data.description: This beautiful home features a Brick and Vinyl exterior, giving it a classic and low-maintenance appeal. The roof was recently replaced in 2022. Inside, you'll find an open floor plan that creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere with plenty of light. The cathedral ceiling in the main living area adds a sense of grandeur and openness. The kitchen is the heart of the home, complete with a stylish kitchen island that provides additional counter space. It is equipped with stainless steel appliances, track lighting and a separate pantry. The entire home features beautiful tile flooring, providing a clean and elegant look throughout. The wood-burning tile fireplace in the living room creates a cozy and warm ambiance, perfect for those chilly evenings. The French doors lead to a privacy-fence back yard. Outside, you'll find a large back paver patio, perfect for outdoor entertaining and enjoying the beautiful weather. Low annual HOA fees that care for the street lights and common area landscaping. Overall, this Brick and Vinyl Home offers a combination of style, functionality, and comfort.
